<section class="slice-sm sct-color-1">
  <div class="profile">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row cols-xs-space cols-sm-space cols-md-space">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="sidebar sidebar--style-2 no-border">
            <div class="widget">
              <!-- Profile picture -->
              <div class="profile-picture profile-picture--style-2">
                <%= image_tag("prv/people/person-7.jpg", class: "img-center") %>
                <a href="#" class="btn-aux">
                  <i class="ion ion-edit"></i>
                </a>
              </div>

              <!-- Profile details -->
              <div class="profile-details">
                <h2 class="heading heading-4 strong-500 profile-name">
                  <%= "#{@profile.first_name} #{@profile.last_name}" %>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="heading heading-6 strong-400 profile-occupation mt-3">Founder, Web Developer</h3>
                <h3 class="heading heading-light heading-6 strong-400 profile-location">Bucharest, Romania</h3>
              </div>

              <!-- Profile stats -->
              <div class="profile-stats clearfix">
                <div class="stats-entry">
                  <span class="stats-count">180</span>
                  <span class="stats-label text-uppercase">Locations</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stats-entry">
                  <span class="stats-count">4.9/5</span>
                  <span class="stats-label text-uppercase">Note</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="profile-connect">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-block btn-rounded btn-base-4 btn-styled-custom">Envoyer un message</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <div class="main-content">
            <!-- Page title -->
            <div class="page-title">
              <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-12">
                  <h2 class="heading heading-5 text-capitalize strong-500 mb-0">
                    <a href="#" class="link text-underline--none">
                      <i class="ion-ios-arrow-back"></i> Profil
                    </a>
                  </h2>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="link-menu link-menu--style-3 py-4 border-bottom">
              <a href="../../pages/profile/account-settings.html" class="active">Profil</a>
              <!--
              <a href="../../pages/profile/account-orders.html">Orders</a>
              <a href="../../pages/profile/account-cards.html">Cards</a>
              <a href="../../pages/profile/account-security.html">Security</a>
              <a href="../../pages/profile/account-connections.html">Connections</a>
-->
            </div>

            <!-- Account settings -->
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <!-- General information -->
                <div class="card no-border bg-transparent">
                  <div class="card-title px-0 pb-0 no-border">
                    <h3 class="heading heading-6 strong-600">
                      Description
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 mb-0">
                      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus lacinia euismod dolor a porttitor. Fusce auctor sit amet odio nec lacinia. Duis ultrices, urna at aliquam auctor, sapien arcu aliquam magna, vitae sollicitudin purus dui sit amet diam. Fusce vitae mollis neque. Vivamus porttitor, eros sed semper maximus, mauris purus hendrerit velit, nec aliquet augue massa consequat lorem. Maecenas in augue maximus, faucibus nisi nec, suscipit justo. In mollis nulla nec ullamcorper blandit. Fusce ut bibendum erat. Curabitur non nunc nunc. Nunc condimentum lectus non nunc convallis, nec auctor lacus sagittis. Donec lacus nibh, lobortis quis accumsan vel, aliquet id nulla. Praesent et ipsum semper, ornare tellus at, convallis lectus.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="mt-0 mb-0">

                <!-- Account info -->
                <div class="card no-border bg-transparent">
                  <div class="card-title px-0 pb-0 no-border">
                    <h3 class="heading heading-6 strong-600">
                      Mat√©riel disponible
                    </h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body px-0">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                      <% 5.times do |i| %>
                      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="block product no-border z-depth-2-top z-depth-2--hover">
                          <div class="block-image">
                            <a href="#">
                              <%= image_tag("boitier/lumix DC-GH5SE.png", class: "img-center") %>
